{
  "stem": "18654.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I never had far to go to school because it was literally next door.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My sister and I went to that school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think I was really told.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just know we moved, that's all I seem to remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think my parents told us-- told me, anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Perhaps-- perhaps Inge knew more because she was a bit older than me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I probably was quite childish, seven and eight years old, because I was the little one of the family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With other relatives.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- my mother was one of four sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe they all lived in this little block of flats.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the husbands that were remaining lived there and their children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't honestly remember too much who lived there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My grandfather lived with us, definitely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think an uncle lived in our flat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think my grandfather, my uncle, my mother, and my father, my sister and I, lived in that flat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think there was even somebody else, but I don't know who it was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I can't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the rest were spread out in the rest of the--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh no, they all moved because of the, because of having to-- You see, my whole family lived in villages.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were pockets of Jews in these little villages all around Frankfurt, and all quite-- I don't know how they managed to survive there, because there were small pockets of Jews that were very quite traditional Jews.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I know I used to visit my aunts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Perhaps for Pesach, I would go there, or one of the other Jewish festivals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were all living within probably a 30 mile radius of each other, because nobody moved too far in those days.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
